    <ul>Are you tired of searching for the same person over and over, trying to find his or her "reappearance?"<br><br>Would you like to know right away if someone moves, files a bankruptcy or has a significant change in their assets?<br><br>If so, try the new Accurint Watchdog.&nbsp;&nbsp;Simply submit a file and Accurint will notify you every week of changes in name, address, phone, bankruptcy, property ownership, motor vehicle registration and death.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Watchdog Wizard will guide you through a simple step-by-step process to save you time that you can spend on more important work.</ul>
